{"tid":1815310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藥房趁火打劫，一盒外科口罩賣498元","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T15:56:03.000Z","uid":36494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4f34ab3665e8b6ed6d5a983f419e1334e83c95da","tid":1815310,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"【旺角有藥房大幅加價 50個口罩賣498元】<br />\n<br />\n武漢爆發不明肺炎，從武漢回港須通報的個案增至三十宗，口罩又成為搶手貨。在旺角，有藥房將口罩放在當眼地方售賣，一盒50個的外科口罩賣498元，平均一個口罩價值近十元。不願意透露身分的負責人指，早前仍賣50元一盒外科口罩，即使加至近500元一盒，一天內仍賣出約一百盒。<br />\n<br />\n藥房負責人指，加價是因為來貨價上升，但沒透露升幅。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #藥房 #口罩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪想被人裝修？"},{"pid":"68cea1bc018264b0ab0f402f14902e9e504644db","tid":1815310,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"上水走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立   唯一出路</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國肺炎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d937e49b4697f27887ef2648c9352ca44a0cc","tid":1815310,"uid":318123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"唔使裝修 罷買咪得囉"},{"pid":"3a6ae015fcc06adf6d198714d95aaf0489cc8be7","tid":1815310,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"呢D真係人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5075bb2d8f6762281789a196e0f2245b458a71fa","tid":1815310,"uid":27395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:08:27.000Z","msg":"陰質錢"},{"pid":"71ad9943d89b4320f44015a5509dc2841138f231","tid":1815310,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4ead5af9b3d955a352416730987b8e9aaefbd3d","tid":1815310,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n環保口罩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d6e7375e517991c9dfc13987d911a4bd8512fc2a","tid":1815310,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"【借位，與主題無關】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試下用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有普選，唯有獨立」</span></strong>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"8c922edd5f9a3162104b7ce1fb1b13e6400c9579","tid":1815310,"uid":262834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"有口罩有閪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e402b9fd687c360b9945133e5b6ba133ed26df6","tid":1815310,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce502993f1173a45050e89e6ec066f7697f67d7","tid":1815310,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"5舊水仲賣到100盒<br />\n香港人真係癲架"},{"pid":"ab1ed70a84e25e685d0a52c333b800b0a35611d5","tid":1815310,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8d937e49b4697f27887ef2648c9352ca44a0cc","tid":1815310,"uid":318123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1